 Faze Nigerian singer Chibuzor Oji better known as Faze has lost his twin sister two days to there birthday. Faze took to his Instagram page on Monday, February 22, 2021, where he announced the demise of his twin sister. Sharing a video of compiled photos of his late sister, he wrote; “It’s a sad day. My Twin sister has left me just two days to our birthday. We the Oji family take strength in knowing that she’ll never have to deal with this world’s problems anymore. We know she’s in a better place now,” View this post on Instagram A post shared by FAZE (@fazealone)